name: Supplier
text: P^4h^4e^4w.^2.^2.^2just loaded up three palettes of water out back for you guys.

name: Cashier
text: How many bottles in a palette again?

name: Supplier
text: That's over 5000 water bottles.^9 Nearly threw out my back lugging them all in.

name: Cashier
text: Wow.^9 Thanks again for bringing that in.^9 Take care of yourself,^5 and go easier on your back,^5 alright?
